4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks, encompassing 3 live online classes per week with a maximum of 16 participants. It covers essential topics such as Windows, Linux, network and server administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. Students will also learn risk management with a focus on data loss prevention strategies and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, participants receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop